
 On UNIX build with :
     UNIX> <setup osc_vis kit>
 test that osc-config is here with :
     UNIX> osc-config
 then build with :
     UNIX> chmod a+x build
     UNIX> ./build
 set the PYTHONPATH with :
      csh> source setup.csh
    (  sh> source setup.sh )
 and run with :
     UNIX> osc-gui-viewer ../scripts/OnX/main.onx

 On Windows build with :
      DOS> <setup osc_vis kit>
 test that osc-config is here with :
      DOS> osc-config
 test that VisualC++ is here with :
      DOS> cl.exe
 then build with :
      DOS> call build.bat
 set the PYTHONPATH with :
      DOS> call setup.bat
 and run with :
      DOS> osc-gui-viewer ..\scripts\OnX\main.onx

